<!doctype html>
<html>
    <head>
        <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="favicon.png" />
        <title>How Many Times Has The House Voted to Repeal Obamacare?</title>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="http://netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
        <style type="text/css">
.howmany {
    padding: 5% 0 5% 0;
    text-align: center;
}

.howmany h1 {
    font-size: 1000%;
}

.footnotes {
    margin-top: 20em;
}

.ref {
    font-size: 66%;
    vertical-align: text-top;
}

.footnotes {
    font-size: 80%;
}

a {
    color: black;
}

a:hover {
    text-decoration: none;
}

a[href] {
    color: #428BCA;
}

#footer p {
    font-size: 60%;
    margin: 1em 0 0 0;
}

.democrat {
    color: blue;
}

.republican {
    color: red;
}

.independent {
    color: #DEC509;
}

.nowrap {
    white-space:nowrap;
}

.data-table {
    font-size: 80%;
}

.vote-table tbody tr td {
    padding: 4px;
    border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
}

h2 {
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
}

ul.affiliation-list,
ul.resolution-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0.5em;
}

ul.affiliation-list li,
ul.resolution-list li {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: inline;
}
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="howmany col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
                    <h1>{{count}}</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
                    <p>As of {{last_update.strftime("%B %d, %Y")}}, the United States House of Representatives has considered <strong>{{count}}</strong> times to repeal the Patient Protection and
                    Affordable Care Act (better known as Obamacare<a class="ref" href="#ref1">[1]</a>).</p>
                    <p>The GOP-led House has also shut down the U.S. federal government for the first time in 17 years, and failed to meet <del>m</del>any of their basic obligations. But, hey, at
                    least they can vote dozens of times to repeal a perfectly constitutional law<a class="ref" href="#ref2">[2]</a> which, while strictly worse than a conventional single-payer system,
                    will immensely help their non-insurance-company owning constituents.</p>
                    <p>Estimating half a day for each passage, this translates to <strong>{{ "${:,.2f}".format(cost) }}</strong> in salary for the esteemed Representatives to waste their, their
                    consituents', and their country's time.<a class="ref" href="#ref3">[3]</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <h2>The Resolutions</h2>
                <table class="table table-responsive table-hover data-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Introduced</th>
                            <th>Bill ID</th>
                            <th>Title</th>
                            <th>Votes</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        {% for repeal in repeals %}
                        <tr>
                            <td class="nowrap">{{repeal.date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d')}}</td>
                            <td><a id="res-{{repeal.bill_id}}" href="https://www.congress.gov/bill/{{repeal.congress}}th-congress/house-bill/{{repeal.resolution.number}}">{{repeal.bill_id}}</a></td>
                            {% if repeal.resolution.short_title %}
                            <td><abbr title="{{repeal.resolution.official_title}}">{{repeal.resolution.short_title}}</abbr></td>
                            {% else %}
                            <td>{{repeal.resolution.official_title}}</td>
                            {% endif %}
                            {% if repeal.vote %}
                            <td><table class="vote-table">
                                {% for result, parties in repeal.vote.by_party.items() %}
                                <tr>
                                    <td>{{result}}</td>
                                    {% for party in ALL_PARTIES %}
                                    {% set party_full = PARTY_MAP[party] %}
                                    <td class="{{party_full}}">{{parties.get(party, 0)}}</td>
                                    {% endfor %}
                                </tr>
                                {% endfor %}
                            </table>
                            </td>
                            {% else %}
                            <td></td>
                            {% endif %}
                        </tr>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <h2>The Sponsors</h2>
                <table class="table table-responsive table-hover data-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Bills Sponsored/Co-sponsored</th>
                            <th>Name</th>
                            <th></th>
                            <th></th>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        {% for sponsor_id, resolutions in sponsors %}
                        {% set legislator = legislators_by_thomas_id[sponsor_id] %}
                        {% if legislator.name.official_full %}
                            {% set lname = legislator.name.official_full %}
                        {% else %}
                            {% set lname = legislator.name.first + " " + legislator.name.last %}
                        {% endif %}
                        <tr>
                            <td>{{resolutions | count}}</td>
                            {% if legislator.id.bioguide %}
                            <td><a href="http://bioguide.congress.gov/scripts/biodisplay.pl?index={{legislator.id.bioguide}}">{{lname}}</a></td>
                            {% else %}
                            <td>{{lname}}
                            {% endif %}
                            <td><ul class="nowrap affiliation-list">
                                {% for affiliation in legislator_affiliations[sponsor_id] %}
                                {% set astyle=PARTY_MAP[affiliation[0]] %}
                                <li class="{{astyle}}">{{affiliation}}</li>
                                {% endfor %}
                            </ul></td>
                            <td><ul class="resolution-list">
                                {% for resolution in resolutions %}
                                <li><a href="#res-{{resolution}}">{{resolution}}</a></li>
                                {% endfor %}
                            </ul></td>
                        </tr>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            <div class="row footnotes">
                <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
                    <ol>
                        <li><a id="ref1" href="http://www.cnn.com/2012/06/25/politics/obamacare-word-debate/index.html">http://www.cnn.com/2012/06/25/politics/obamacare-word-debate/index.html</a></li>
                        <li><a id="ref2" href="http://www.supremecourt.gov/opinions/11pdf/11-393c3a2.pdf"><em>National Federation of Independent Business v.  Sebelius</em></a></li>
                        <li><a id="ref3"></a><a href="http://thomas.loc.gov/home/ds/">225 working days per year</a>, <a href="http://usgovinfo.about.com/od/uscongress/a/congresspay.htm">$174,000 salary per representative per year</a>, 435 representatives. Insert multiplication and division operators as needed.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="footer" class="credit">
                <p>Created and updated by James Brown (<a
                    href="https://www.roguelazer.com">roguelazer.com</a>).
                All errors are my own.
                </p>
                <p>Data source from <a href="https://www.govtrack.us">GovTrack.us</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
